In the Source Files folder named 21301AnimAsset, I have also provided a body animation UAsset

25
00:02:32.899 --> 00:02:35.219
file.

26
00:02:35.219 --> 00:02:40.899
If at any point you need to reference the location of the course map, that can be found

27
00:02:40.900 --> 00:02:45.140
